title: The Miz, The Terror of The Tank, and There Are No Rich & Famous Bald Men
description:
Subscribe, Rate, and Leave a Review! - Election Recap - (26:00) Four Seasons Mixup - (31:30) Who's back of the Week - (54:00)The Feed Willie Burger controversy - Frank the Tank terrorized us during Stool Streams Jenga - (01:11:00)Top 5 Alex Trebek Moments - (01:33:30) Voicemails (01:56:00) The Miz joins the show.
